# CODEOWNERS. GitHub applies the LAST matching pattern, and owners do NOT
# accumulate across patterns, so rules are ordered least-specific first and any
# file that needs several owners lists them all on its own line.
#
# Every schema is owned by SRE together with the component's current owner, so a
# schema change notifies both.

# Default maintainer.
* @jasagredo

